      "content": "It sounds like you are experiencing a profound sense of detachment and pervasive numbness right now, which can feel incredibly isolating. These feelings of dissociation and quiet emptiness are distressing, and it's important to know you don't have to carry this weight alone. Please consider reaching out to a mental health professional or a crisis line to talk through these intense sensations. You deserve support to help you find a way back to feeling grounded and connected.",
